I recently installed the USI mod onto my computer in the game data folder and when I created a new save file and went into the VAB, I only saw the drills  under new industry part filter. There was no other parts but the drills and all the drills were gray with no variation. Did I install the mod wrong or what cause I am really struggling to figure this one out.

Thanks
